# **Therapy Session Analysis App**  

## **Overview**  
The Therapy Session Analysis App is designed to streamline therapy workflows by automating key tasks, allowing therapists to focus on patient interaction rather than administrative work.  

## **Key Features**  
- **Speaker Identification** â€“ Differentiates between therapist and patient in recorded audio sessions.  
- **Speech-to-Text Conversion** â€“ Accurately transcribes spoken dialogue into text.  
- **Progressive Note Generation** â€“ Produces refined session notes with key insights, sentiment analysis, and summaries.  
- **Intelligent Suggestions** â€“ Uses NLP and LLMs to provide real-time or post-session prompts, resources, and intervention recommendations.  

## **Technologies Used**  
- **Deep Learning Models** â€“ For speaker identification.  
- **Automatic Speech Recognition (ASR)** â€“ For speech-to-text conversion.  
- **Natural Language Processing (NLP)** â€“ For text analysis and summarization.  
- **Large Language Models (LLMs)** â€“ For intelligent suggestion generation and retrieval.  

## **Benefits**  
âœ… **Increased Efficiency** â€“ Reduces therapists' time spent on manual transcription and note-taking.  
